If you like the idea click ⭐ on the repo and stay tuned. 

Add awesome xonshrc to the end of current xonshrc:

    curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/anki-code/awesome-xonshrc/main/xonshrc >> ~/.xonshrc

